<!-- Our Story Section -->
<section id="about">
    <div class="mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="bg-primary-50 text-white pt-5 pb-10 md:pt-20 md:pb-20 px-4 md:px-15 text-center text-lg md:text-xl">
                <h2 class="text-3xl text-primary-800 font-semibold text-center mb-8">Our Story</h2>
                <div class="prose prose-lg text-base max-w-none text-textcolor-950">
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        Kailash Research Foundation (KRF) was born out of a legacy quietly built, not declared. My
                        grandparents believed that the most profound impact is made not through words, but through the
                        way one lives. Their lives were defined by acts of generosity and integrity that asked for no
                        recognition, yet left deep, lasting imprints on the people around them. KRF is my way of
                        carrying forward that tradition, grounded in altruism, sustained by action.
                    </p>
                    <p class="mb-4">
                        On the field, these challenges never stand alone — they are intertwined with caste, religion,
                        and social inequities, creating complex realities that demand solutions built on a scientific
                        approach and a deep understanding of people's lived realities.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        KRF rests on a simple belief: change is not enough — evolution is the goal. change makes things
                        work a little better; evolution reshapes them so they no longer carry the same flaws. Our work
                        is to design systems that are inclusive, resilient, and built to endure — systems that not only
                        resolve today's challenges but open the way for communities to thrive on their own in the
                        future.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white flex flex-col justify-center items-start p-10">
                <div class="bg-red-100 w-9/10 mx-auto md:w-full ring-1 ring-primary-800 px-10 py-5 md:py-10 text-primary-950" style="background-color: #f7f4d5">
                    <p class="text-2xl md:text-4xl text-center mb-3 md:mb-6 text-primary-800 font-semibold">Our Vision</p>

                    <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl italic text-center mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                        "At KRF, we believe that <span class="font-medium text-primary-600">transformation is strongest when it is grounded in both insight and action</span>. Our mission is to bridge the gap between the realities communities face and the solutions they deserve, creating systems that are as resilient as they are inclusive."
                    </p>

                    <p class="text-md md:text-xl text-center">
                        KRF is our shared platform to unite research, policy, and community action. We see it as a space where ideas evolve into tangible, lasting transformation. If our vision resonates with you, we welcome you to connect, collaborate, and grow alongside us.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
